          <Vi>Đại lộ; đại lộ rộng, có cây xanh hai bên</Vi>
          <En>A wide, tree-lined street, typically in a city, often with a median or central reservation.</En>
          <Example>They strolled along the boulevard, enjoying the shade of the old oak trees.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
